tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE CalibrationRecord (
   record_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
   equipment_id UUID,
   calibration_date DATE,
   calibration_result VARCHAR(20),
   technician_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE CalibrationLog (
   log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
   record_id UUID,
   technician_id UUID,
   calibration_date DATE,
   calibration_notes TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE CalibrationLog (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    equipment_id INT,
    calibration_date DATE,
    technician_name VARCHAR(50),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE CalibrationHistory (
    history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    equipment_id INT,
    calibration_date DATE,
    calibration_value_before FLOAT,
    calibration_value_after FLOAT
);
